graph TD
    Client[Frontend - React]
    
    subgraph Serviço de Vendas
        Sales[Vendas API - PHP/Laravel]
        DB_Sales[(DB Vendas - PostgreSQL)]
    end
    
    subgraph Serviço de Catálogo
        Catalog[Catálogo API - Python]
        DB_Catalog[(DB Catálogo - PostgreSQL)]
    end

    Client -->|1. GET /eventos| Catalog
    Client -->|2. POST /comprar| Sales
    Sales -->|3. POST /reservar| Catalog
    
    Sales --- DB_Sales
    Catalog --- DB_Catalog